Definitely not ordering at this place again. Extremely sloppy and dirty.

Had to correct the guy serving me on my salad’s ingredients. Went back to look for a cup of water, there were none and the one person working with customers was busy so I asked the two people at the back who said it was at the front. Told them there were none and the lady told me I’d have to ask the one person working, condescendingly. I sat back down and my friend waiting at the table said the two people from the back rolled their eyes and made a face to each other when I walked away (thankfully they saw her catching their rudeness). These employees get annoyed at their customers for very simple small requests, this place needs better management or employees that have a minimum of work ethic. Both other locations I go to (soho and tribeca) are very fast, efficient and pleasant.
